The paper proposes a method for improving disentanglement in VAEs through image preprocessing using regionally aggregated feature maps extracted from CNNs pretrained on ImageNet. This involves techniques from machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of CNNs and feature extraction is a common technique in neural networks (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
